data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home! Large family home in a great location with room to grow, boasting almost 2100 square feet of living space. The roof is just 9 years old, and the HVAC was replaced in 2021.  Home has a formal sunken living room, formal dining room, and large kitchen with eat-in area, open to the family room with wood burning fireplace and soaring cathedral ceilings. The spare bedrooms are spacious with large closets, and the master  bedroom is expansive, with ample room for your bedroom set and a sitting/office area.  The master bathroom shower has been redone, and the master closet is sizable.  There are sliding glass doors going out from the breakfast area that lead to the back patio inside the completely fenced yard.  New owners will enjoy the benefit of knowing that the neighboring lot to the west will remain vacant, as it is owned by the county, and will remain so.  This home needs some updating, but will make someone an absolutley beautiful home....don't miss out!!
